com.privalia.qa.utils

Class BaseGTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.privalia.qa.utils.BaseGTest

  • public abstract class BaseGTest
extends Object
    This is a custom implementation of AbstractTestNGCucumberTests that makes use of the custom CucumberRunner class. Test classes must extend this class in order to be executed with TestNG and use the library steps
    Author:
    Jose Fernandez
